sub_title: Researcher in Machine Learning, Data Science architect
summary:
I love to work on challenging technical problems, and lead the implementation of solutions that actually solve the problems of the customers. Pushing the envelope with innovative new techniques, drawing on a strong technical background in both mathematics and machine learning, but also always looking towards the business side: is this what is really helping the customer?
Always looking for new things to learn, constantly trying to improve myself.
